01:14:09.760 --> 01:14:10.960
professional game critics

01:14:10.960 --> 01:14:11.680
are quite often

01:14:11.680 --> 01:14:12.800
more ahead of the curb

01:14:12.800 --> 01:14:14.000
than the average consumer

01:14:14.000 --> 01:14:15.760
or the not-to-be-rude

01:14:15.760 --> 01:14:16.720
fanboy types

01:14:16.720 --> 01:14:18.000
who will dismiss a sequel

01:14:18.000 --> 01:14:18.960
for being too different

01:14:18.960 --> 01:14:19.840
to the one they first

01:14:19.840 --> 01:14:20.880
fell in love with.

01:14:20.880 --> 01:14:22.160
Mainstream game critics

01:14:22.160 --> 01:14:23.200
can be wrong,

01:14:23.200 --> 01:14:24.640
but they've been consistently

01:14:24.640 --> 01:14:26.000
right about the Souls series

01:14:26.000 --> 01:14:27.360
from day one.

01:14:27.360 --> 01:14:28.800
It's only corners of the internet

01:14:28.800 --> 01:14:30.720
full of rose-tinted fanboyishness

01:14:30.720 --> 01:14:32.080
towards the first Dark Souls

01:14:32.080 --> 01:14:33.680
that result in the ridiculous

01:14:33.680 --> 01:14:35.200
treatment of the second game.

01:14:35.200 --> 01:14:36.400
When it comes down to it,

01:14:36.400 --> 01:14:37.600
Dark Souls was

01:14:37.600 --> 01:14:38.720
a fantastic game,

01:14:38.720 --> 01:14:39.520
even though it's flawed

01:14:39.520 --> 01:14:40.160
in a lot of ways

01:14:40.160 --> 01:14:41.280
that are so much more obvious

01:14:41.280 --> 01:14:42.240
now than ever.

01:14:42.240 --> 01:14:43.600
I think the sheer surprise

01:14:43.600 --> 01:14:45.040
of how good Dark Souls was

01:14:45.040 --> 01:14:45.760
after most people

01:14:45.760 --> 01:14:47.280
missed the boat on Demon's Souls

01:14:47.280 --> 01:14:48.720
made it a hard act to follow

01:14:48.720 --> 01:14:49.760
and lots of fans got

01:14:49.760 --> 01:14:51.920
unrealistic expectations about it.

01:14:51.920 --> 01:14:53.680
The online response to Dark Souls 3

01:14:53.680 --> 01:14:55.040
sounds overall lukewarm

01:14:55.040 --> 01:14:55.920
but positive,

01:14:55.920 --> 01:14:57.200
