01:14:57.200 --> 01:14:59.360
at least in regards to this one series,

01:14:59.360 --> 01:15:00.800
maybe not a couple others,

01:15:00.800 --> 01:15:01.680
people have cooled

01:15:01.760 --> 01:15:02.640
and learned to manage

01:15:02.640 --> 01:15:03.920
their expectations.

01:15:03.920 --> 01:15:04.960
I'm interested in finally

01:15:04.960 --> 01:15:05.520
getting to play it

01:15:05.520 --> 01:15:06.560
