01:15:10.000 --> 01:15:10.960
to some aspects of 2

01:15:10.960 --> 01:15:11.920
made them walk back

01:15:11.920 --> 01:15:12.720
on the good ideas

01:15:12.720 --> 01:15:13.840
in an effort to be more like

01:15:13.840 --> 01:15:14.640
the first one,

01:15:14.640 --> 01:15:15.600
but I'm gonna play it

01:15:15.600 --> 01:15:16.800
and judge it on its own merits

01:15:16.800 --> 01:15:17.520
as its own game

01:15:17.520 --> 01:15:19.120
before I really consider that.

01:15:19.120 --> 01:15:20.400
In the meantime,

01:15:20.400 --> 01:15:22.240
Dark Souls 2 is not perfect,

01:15:22.240 --> 01:15:22.880
but you can have

01:15:22.880 --> 01:15:24.240
a grand old time with it.

01:15:24.240 --> 01:15:25.200
The gameplay contains

01:15:25.200 --> 01:15:26.320
some of the tightest moments

01:15:26.320 --> 01:15:27.520
in the whole series

01:15:27.520 --> 01:15:29.120
and some really fun variations

01:15:29.120 --> 01:15:30.080
on the formula.

01:15:30.080 --> 01:15:30.880
It tells a story

01:15:30.880 --> 01:15:31.920
that instead of redoing

01:15:31.920 --> 01:15:32.560
the original

01:15:32.560 --> 01:15:33.520
or trying to build on it

01:15:33.520 --> 01:15:34.880
in a straightforward way,

01:15:34.880 --> 01:15:36.160
self-consciously explores

01:15:36.160 --> 01:15:37.280
what it means to exist

01:15:37.280 --> 01:15:38.480
in a specific position

01:15:38.480 --> 01:15:39.760
in gaming culture

01:15:39.760 --> 01:15:40.560
and asks us

01:15:40.560 --> 01:15:41.680
what the things we desire

01:15:41.680 --> 01:15:42.480
from games

01:15:42.480 --> 01:15:43.680
say about us.

01:15:43.680 --> 01:15:45.520
I really enjoyed Dark Souls 2,

01:15:45.520 --> 01:15:46.800
and I think there's a lot of things

01:15:46.800 --> 01:15:47.680
that make it good,

01:15:47.680 --> 01:15:49.120
and if you didn't enjoy it,

01:15:49.120 --> 01:15:50.160
that's okay.

01:15:50.160 --> 01:15:51.200
Your different opinions

01:15:51.200 --> 01:15:52.000
and experiences

01:15:52.000 --> 01:15:53.040
